text: tavada sæbævinma api isrāīl daruvan va sæbǣ vāsasthāna vala padiṁci kerevvemu. tavada yahapat dæyin api ovunaṭa pōṣaṇaya labā dunimu. ovun veta gnānaya pæmiṇena tek ovuhu mata bhēda æti kara nogatha. ovun kavara viṣayaka mata bhēda vemin siṭiyē da ē sambandhayen maḷavun keren nægiṭuvanu labana dinayē num̆bagē paramādhipati niyata vaśayenma ovun atara tīndu denu æta
